reviews.review_text: Convenient location. It was very clean inside. Staff are nice. Everything else pretty McDonalds standard
I m so fat but I don t care I come here every day and order 6 Big Macs 9 fries 4 cokes 2 chicken nuggets and 0 quarter pounders. I love this place and I will go to it until I can t no more

As of the last 4 months something changed. You ask for fresh burger at the drive through...you used to get fresh! NOW. you drive away and you find your burger is not fresh...maybe because theyre hoping you drive away not notice. This place was a total 10....now a 5 Parking: These guys allow costco people to park in their lot....theres so much space

The staff were all over it. They endure a lot from the customers,  but still work hard to keep us happy! The prices here are far and away the best and the food tastes good. Tip your hats to all working here. Outstanding. October 2023 - no changes here! Restaurant is very clean. Orders are going through very promptly. Staff are engaged, efficient and courteous. Still seats, but maybe 80%full. Compared to other outlets in the area, this one is twice the others, in all categories. Always a pleasure to come here!
The best sosig egg mcmuff I ve ever had! Add fresh tomato recommended

Recently renovated with a clean and relaxing atmosphere. Regular spot for Costco shoppers while waiting. They have changed the kids play area to a much smaller space and adding party and meeting room.

Just ate at this location on 16 February 2021. Service was amazingly prompt on a complicated order, and all 3 of the staff i met were truly friendly. Whole establishment including washrooms are kept ultra clean.  This location is conveniently located by a Costco and SaveOnFoods and other stores. Spacious free parking too.

5 stars for the kiosks! Never had to line up for them, and its much faster than paying and ordering at the cashier. There is also an indoor playground my kid enjoys as well. Overall, very convenient for families with impatient, hungry kids.
I barely go to Mac. Here for BTS meal, thats all
Best McDonalds in all of Pitt Meadows, Port Coquitlam and Coquitlam.

No issues. Cat returned happy and healthy. For the price, very happy. Cat got a large cage that allowed both indoor and outdoor living. Close to home. Good value. Have tried two others. One was also close to home and price was ok, but cage was small. The other was probably my favorite but double the cost and not close to home. Large style cage but more of a cat hotel. No outside access though.
Always well prepared breakfast sandwiches and fresh coffee!

The best place to go when I want late snack, especially after midnight. If they can turn up the air conditioning during will be the best. I always come when my folks are shopping in Costco. Staff are polite and they clean up all the time.i think this MacDonald is the best one in TriCity area.

Am not fan of fast food but Its McDonalds, you know what to expect food-wise. This place has a huge kids play area, which is probably a big reason why so many people comes here. There isnt enough room for the lineups, so a crowd often forms by the pop dispenser. I guess they didnt plan on always being so busy. If youre in a hurry, KFC/Taco Bell across the street never has a line.
This place is really busy during the day but the food is really consistent. Ice cream machine tends to break overnight... Food
My son loves the playroom

All around good service but worth leaving a comment because the girl cleaning the tables was really nice and chatty (yet productive) and just really great. She had a brace on her wrist and said it was an injury from the repetitive motion of wiping tables. Despite this she was still super positive. She single handedly made my bad day better. McDonalds: give her a raise!

Always good service here, orders are fulfilled accurately, and rarely have to wait too long in the drive through.  Play place is ok, it could benefit from more frequent cleaning, but its nice and bright with all the windows.
Nice clean, good location, plenty of parking, food in general is standard McDonalds fast food

This McDonalds ROCKS!!!!! The service here is impeccable! These guys took our large order for 10 and made ZERO MISTAKES ... They even got our ketchup right. We were really impressed. So if youre looking for that crisp Golden Arches, look no further than this McDonalds!!
Very good place thre is s place where kids can play and enjoy u must visit.!! Parking: Verg large place to park Food : 5/5 |

I just downloaded the new ordering app so it took some time to get used to it but once I placed the order, I arrived at the store few minutes later and my order was ready, the staff is very professional amidst this covid and they tended to everyone who was waiting outside :) food is fresh and well done!

This is a good mcdonalds location. Parking is sometimes a bit limited due the costco next door but Ive never been unable to find parking. This location has an excellent play structure that I would say are best for 3+ year olds.
Kids love the play area lots of fun but can get pretty busy. Self order kiosk is always fun for the kids but definitely slower then ordering from the til.
Very quick and efficient, didnt have to wait on the sidelines for our food this time. Always happy about that
Bring my grandson here every weekend and the drive tru staff are always so kind to him. Good food, fast service keep it up!
The chicken wraps are good.

At McDonalds, predictability is what we count on. However, even as a chain, they provide excellent service such as in table order and mobile pickup, things that we grew expecting from every restaurant. Unfortunately not many provide that and that is what makes McDonalds shine.
good deal for a $3 big Mac
Love the indoor playground. My child enjoyed a lot with the happy meal. Perfect to stay with your energetic child when it s rainy or cold

I bought the Cayenne GTS through Mr. William Fong four years ago, and it felt great to buy a car -- use a car -- to maintain it. Willam, very warm, attentive and meticulous. In these 4 years every maintenance, tire change, home suspension insurance and so on all look for him, all easy. Id like to come by and have a look at the new car when I have time. The coffee here is very good, I love Porsche.
One of our family favorites food locations. It has a playing area for small kids. The drive thru is always busy. Always fast service and the staff are friendly.

The WiFi is strong enough to watch YouTube in your parked vehicle and the breakfast mcmuffin is 10 cent lower than other locations. The human rights court of B.C has ordered McDonalds to not order their employees to wash their hands!!!
I was  at this location yesterday and it was really clean and tidy! Plus I got my food at a fast speed and the order was correct!
The employees are friendly, kind and helpful to the customers. I have been in other Macdonalds locations and the they are not all the same.
Same taste as always, well cooked meal, great service, the clerk even advised me to buy a cheaper combination for what I wanted. I really like this place.
Once on a while is ok to have a chest day!! You must try the BLT grilled chicken without Mayo and add habanero sauce! Yum yum!!!
Fast, accurate and fresh (: usually this late at night the food is cold and not fresh! Great job! The guy working drive true was very friendly.
Good service, big play place. The manager walks around with a pot of coffee and gives people refills at their seats. One of the better McDonalds for sure.
Best manager ever seen . So friendly and responsible..
Most McDonalds are sloppy, slow and dont really care> This is my go-to McDonalds when Im feeling it- they are all super friendly and everything is almost always made fresh. Wouldnt go anywhere else.
Very good quality meals, I eat every single day here. And you might see me inside too (workng).
Its mc Donalds. The food is what it is; but they dont mess my order up and they always give me napkins. So hence you get 5 stars mcdickz
Great mcdonalds location here. The staff are always so fast and friendly. Highly recommend this spot.
I picked what I want and buy from almost like ATM better than go to cashier.
The automated order system is amazing, fast and saves a lot of time
McDoubles are simple but this McDonald s actually seasons the meat. It s noticed
Great big Mac and poutine combo is exactly what I want
Surprisingly fast and accurate service, compared to some other McDonalds stores Ive been to.
Friendly Staff! Covid Safe!
Very clean and nice site. Outside tables are clean, flowers around. Liked it
They got the minion toy in the happy meal less gooo
Just comin from Boston Pizza , a few dudes were late arrivals and had a taste for Quarter Pounders .... Good burgers and juicy.....
There is not bad size kids playground, just perfect for rainy days.
A great place to bring your kids, has a great play center and the food is pretty good too, also perpared well.
Always clean, staff are friendly and helpful
Lots of options and good amount of fruit/potatoes.
Our home on rainy days. Awesome play pace inside for kids.  Always great service with the staff inside.
Favorite forever.  Service has improved lately.
I just had the best mcflurry of all time.  Lots of sauce and lots of m&Ms.  Way to go flurry dude!
Made a request and they were very understanding.  Better than the avg Mcdonald.
Excellent place to grab breakfast, great group of people working here. A+++ DEFINITELY RECOMMEND THIS PLACE
Had to have some food because we were moving our house the whole day so really good for a late night bite.
This time I used the drive thur and we found a very nice service even in this difficult time with the virus 19
This McDonalds is consistently pretty fast to complete your order, and many of the staff are quite friendly.
Gets my order right every time, quick consistent staff!
This location has a good play area, and now has kiosk ordering. Ample and easy parking.
Ive been at this location quite a few times. Hands down friendliest customer service Ive experienced at any location
Its mcd LOL
Good food and friendly staff and amazing play ground  for my little girls.
Great food nice and kind staff who know my order by heart
Great service during school rush.
Young staff but they try. Ill miss $1 coffees. Still good at $2.
Whatever your ordering ask for freshly made. Very nice staff.
Close to Costco and have kids playground inside. Clean and tasty food.
Very nice place.  The staff is friendly and its covid safe
Nice, clean location. Can be busy at times, but not generally overflowing.
Tried other locations for the same order and this location is still the best!
The kids like the playing area here
Summer drink days paid 2 bucks for a vanilla chai frappe
$1 Ice coffee worth 5 stars alone!
It is very delicious especially there fries
Nearby location for early breakfast. good luck guys.
Fast and polite service especially in the drive-thru.
Always fast and clean service. Close to home Depot and Costco too!
Great location
Friendly, efficient staff.  Restaurant is nice and clean.
Honestly, the friendliest McDonalds staff Ive ever encountered.
Good coffee. Family friendly with fast drive through
Drive through fast and delicious sundaes and warm apple pies.
Real good Biryni dishes and Zaika Kadhai lamb as well
Fast and when orders are not correct they are prompt to rectify
Its always a good quick meal!!
Price is same or similar to BC liquor store.
Quick snack after a round of golf at Carnustie golf club
Cant go wrong with fresh hot mcdonalds fries
Good food. Quick. Relaxing atmosphere.
I mean... its McDonalds.
Only used the bathroom. Thank you!
Very good and fast McDonalds
